Date and Time: Wednesday, August 20, 2025, 7:00 PM – 9:00 PM CEST
Location: Virtual (Livestreamed on the BuildOnBase X account: https://x.com/buildonbase
)
Host: BuildOnBase
Purpose: Learn to implement gasless transactions and build two hands-on projects: converting a standard app into a Mini App and customizing a forked Mini App for deployment.
Registration: Free via https://lu.ma/vdoipqa8

This event is part of Vibe Coding Week, a series designed to empower developers with the tools and knowledge to create cutting-edge decentralized applications (dApps) on Base, a layer-2 scaling solution for Ethereum. Day 3 focuses on the “Based” stack, showcasing features like Smart Accounts, OnchainKit, and Paymaster to make your apps more accessible and efficient.

